CRESCENT LIGHTERAGE COMPANY, Owner of THE Barge MAE E., Libelant-Appellee, v. THE Steam Tug MARY MESECK, Meseck Towing Line, and THE McALLISTER NO. 94, Claimant-Appellant. No. 20. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Oct. 17, 1932. Poley & Martin, of New York .City (James A. Martin, of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. William P. Purdy, of New York City (William P. Purdy and John E. Purdy, both, of New York City, of counsel), for appellee.

■ Before MANTON, L. HAND, and SWAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree affirmed.
